							Welcome to the Beginner live courses in Colloquial Tibetan. You'll <strong>learn alongside a global cohort</strong> of classmates from around the world.
						</p>

						<p class="text-lg leading-relaxed mb-6" style="font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif; color: #000; font-size: 14pt;">
							Meet <strong>kind and patient Tibetan tutors</strong> who guide you through every step of your learning journey.
						</p>

						<p class="text-lg leading-relaxed" style="font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif; color: #000; font-size: 14pt;">
